「树莓派」是什么以及普通人怎么玩？ 
https://www.zhihu.com/question/20859055

Try a Linux project with the Pi, and hook it up to Xively
https://personal.xively.com

外网可以访问本地Nginx搭的网站
1.花生壳
2.ngrok(GitHub - inconshreveable/ngrok: Introspected tunnels to localhost)
3.frp(GitHub - fatedier/frp: A fast reverse proxy to help you expose a local server behind a NAT or firewall to the internet.)
你需要有vps
vps装ngrok服务端
pi装ngrok客户端
你可能还需要一个域名，别人访问域名时访问的是你的vps
然后通过ngrok访问你的pi
